An overview will be given on research issues of contemporary biosemiotics: mechanisms of semiosis, typology of semiosis, structure of biological sign systems. Methododological issues of biosemiotics will be discussed, incl. relations between metaphysical and scientific approaches in the history of semiotics and in development of biosemiotics.Objectives/eesmärkid:  An overview will be provided on central studies and contemporary situation of biosemiotics.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Students gain a systematic overview on central discussion on biosemiotics, classical texts and contemporary directions of studies.
